# Retail Sales Performance Dashboard

## Overview
Interactive Power BI dashboard analyzing retail sales data with 1,000+ transactions. Identifies top-performing branches, products, and customer segments.

## Key Insights
- **Total Revenue:** 118.58K
- **Top Branch:** Branch A (70% of total revenue - 82.81K)
- **Top Products:** Shampoo, Orange Juice, Notebook, Detergent, Apple
- **Customer Insight:** Male customers spend 37% more than female customers ($32K vs $23K)

