## Features
- DAX measures for Total Revenue, Total Quantity, and Avg Transaction Value
- Interactive slicers for Branch and Customer Type filtering
- Matrix visual for customer segment analysis (Gender × Customer Type)

## How to View
1. Download the `.pbix` file from this repository
2. Open with Power BI Desktop (free download from Microsoft)
3. Interact with slicers and visuals

## Tools Used
- Power BI Desktop
- DAX (Data Analysis Expressions)
- Power Query for data cleaning

## Data Source
Retail sales dataset from Kaggle (1,000+ transactions, 12 columns)
